<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Backstage Heroes | Volunteer Recognition</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg:            #fcf8f4;
            --white:         #ffffff;
            --rose:          #b83a2e;          /* primary — warm rose red  */
            --rose-light:    #fdf0ee;
            --rose-mid:      #e8786a;
            --teal:          #2d6a5a;          /* secondary — sage teal    */
            --teal-light:    #eaf5f1;
            --amber:         #b8820a;          /* accent — amber gold      */
            --amber-light:   #fef8ec;
            --amber-mid:     #e0a020;
            --lavender:      #7b5ea7;          /* soft lavender */
            --lavender-light: #f5f0fc;
            --ink:           #1c1a18;
            --ink-mid:       #5a5550;
            --mid:           #999;
            --border:        #e8e0d2;
            --shadow:        rgba(28,26,24,0.07);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif; /* A more elegant font for this palette */
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--ink);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        header h1 { 
            color: var(--rose); 
            font-size: 3rem; 
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--ink-mid);
            font-family: sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* The Main Spotlight Card */
        .spotlight-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px var(--shadow);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .hero-image {
            background: var(--rose-light);
            min-height: 450px;
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542601906990-b4d3fb778b09?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800'); /* Sample Nature/Logistics vibe */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            padding: 60px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .main-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--rose-light);
            color: var(--rose);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            width: fit-content;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-name { 
            font-size: 2.8rem; 
            margin: 0; 
            color: var(--ink);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .hero-role { 
            color: var(--teal); 
            font-family: sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600; 
            margin: 15px 0 25px 0; 
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .hero-quote { 
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--ink-mid);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .stat-box { flex: 1; }

        .stat-value { 
            display: block; 
            font-size: 1.5rem; 
            color: var(--rose); 
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .stat-label { 
            font-family: sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.7rem; 
            color: var(--mid); 
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Past Heroes Grid */
        .history-section { margin-top: 40px; }
        .history-header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .past-card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .past-card:hover {
            border-bottom-color: var(--teal);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px var(--shadow);
        }

        .past-name { font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--ink); display: block; }
        .past-date { 
            font-family: sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem; 
            color: var(--lavender); 
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }

        .past-description { color: var(--ink-mid); font-size: 0.95rem; }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .spotlight-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-image { min-height: 300px; }
            .hero-content { padding: 40px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <span class="subtitle">Community Pillars</span>
        <h1>The Backstage Spotlight</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="spotlight-card">
        <div class="hero-image"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="main-badge">Featured Contributor</div>
            <h2 class="hero-name">Alex Chen</h2>
            <div class="hero-role">Logistics & Site Operations</div>
            
            <p class="hero-quote">
                "Finding the right space and ensuring every detail is in place is how I contribute to our collective success."
            </p>

            <div class="stats-row">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-value">12</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Site Recces</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-value">45+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Deliveries</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box" style="color: var(--amber);">
                    <span class="stat-value" style="color: var(--amber);">Gold</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Efficiency</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="history-section">
        <div class="history-header">
            <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight: normal; font-size: 1.8rem;">Previous Heroes</h3>
            <span style="color: var(--mid); font-size: 0.8rem; font-family: sans-serif;">Archives 2026</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="past-card">
                <span class="past-date">MARCH 2026</span>
                <span class="past-name">Sarah Jenkins</span>
                <p class="past-description">Handled the complex financial audits and expense collations for the regional workshop.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="past-card" style="border-bottom-color: var(--lavender-light);">
                <span class="past-date" style="color: var(--teal);">FEBRUARY 2026</span>
                <span class="past-name">Jordan Lee</span>
               <p class="past-description">Coordinated catering and bulk orders for over 200 volunteers during the annual summit.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
